The Security Chief hovered in place.  No appearent activity.  He chuckled to himself, they were definanetly unorganized.  He wanted to see exactly who was down in that little bunker of a base, but the Matrix in his chest could not connect to Vector Sigma in this time.  Could it?
&#39;No, in this time Vector Sigma is still offline.  I won&#39;t be able connect and see who is here.&#39;
&quot;I grow impatient!  Show me some spinal support columns!  Or are you just like the Quintessons, soft and weak?!&quot;
The fusion cannon slowly powered up, and Megatron Revived took aim.  He aimed at a rock formation two hundred yards from the base.
&quot;A thirty percent blast should grab their attention, heh heh heh.&quot;
The cannon powered to thirty percent and the massive blast was issued forth.  The massive violet beam struck the formation and mere seconds later a tremendous explosion rocked the ground.  The tall dust cloud greeted the grinning clone, he never powered up the cannon to this extent.
&quot;Is there anyone home?  Or am I just wasting my time?&quot;

